{# Readiness panel: on-demand webhook 401 self-test. FormBuilder owns the webhook routes, so this
   partial (button + probe controller) lives here and is included by templates/admin/readiness.html.twig
   (loose Twig coupling, like _payment_info). On-demand (button) so the HTTP self-test never slows the
   admin. #}
<div class="card mb-3" data-controller="formbuilder--webhook-check"
     data-formbuilder--webhook-check-url-value="{{ path('form_builder_admin_webhook_check') }}"
     data-formbuilder--webhook-check-csrf-value="{{ csrf_token('webhook_check') }}">
    <div class="card-header">Plaćanja — webhook (basic-auth zamka)</div>
    <div class="card-body">
        <p class="small text-muted mb-2">
            Najčešća go-live zamka: ako je webhook ruta iza basic-autha, plaćanje uspije ali narudžba
            ostane <strong>"U obradi"</strong> (webhook vrati 401 prije aplikacije, bez mailova). Test
            šalje <em>nepotpisani</em> zahtjev na vlastiti webhook URL — prava logika se NE pokreće (potpis
            padne na 400). <strong>401 = problem.</strong> Pokreće se na zahtjev (ne usporava admin).
        </p>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm"
                data-formbuilder--webhook-check-target="button"
                data-action="formbuilder--webhook-check#run">Provjeri webhook (Stripe/PayPal)</button>
        <div class="mt-3" data-formbuilder--webhook-check-target="results"></div>
    </div>
</div>
